title: Pristine Property! Spectacular Ocean Views! 100 Surfsound
text:
Pristine Property! Spectacular Ocean Views! 100 Surfsound ad date: 10/24/2015 
100 Surfsound Court, Smith River, CA Stunning ocean view home on over two acres of pristine property! Panoramic views of CA/OR coast line and St. George Reef lighthouse. This beautiful 2800 Sq. Ft. home features cathedral windows with spectacular ocean views, spacious great room open to dining & kitchen, with a split floor plan. Large master suite with soaking tub, shower & walk-in closet. Enjoy your very own billiards room with wet bar. Pool table conveys w/sale! Property includes a barn, tack room, arena, fruit trees and gorgeous landscape! MLS# 1500521 NOW $599,000
